org.apache.flink.yarn

类 AbstractYarnClusterDescriptor.ApplicationSubmissionContextReflector

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.flink.yarn.AbstractYarnClusterDescriptor.ApplicationSubmissionContextReflector
  • 封闭类:
    AbstractYarnClusterDescriptor

    private static class AbstractYarnClusterDescriptor.ApplicationSubmissionContextReflector
extends java.lang.Object
    Singleton object which uses reflection to determine whether the ApplicationSubmissionContext supports various methods which, depending on the Hadoop version, may or may not be supported.

    If an unsupported method is invoked, nothing happens.

    Currently three methods are proxied: - setApplicationTags (>= 2.4.0) - setAttemptFailuresValidityInterval (>= 2.6.0) - setKeepContainersAcrossApplicationAttempts (>= 2.4.0)
